oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Heiskell Remarks at Funeral of Robert D. Powel
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Address of Joseph B. Heiskell, Esq., delivered at Rogersville, Tennessee, upon the occasion of the funeral of Lieut. Robert D. Powel, who was killed in an engagement with the Tories, at Barbourville, Kentucky, on Thursday morning, September 19, 1861.
